    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルー、ファイ、オー……ファイ、オー……\nはぁ、はぁ、はぁ……",
      "startTime": 4.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 35000,
          "startTime": 35.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bicycle-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "フォームが乱れてるぞ！　もっと胸を張って！\n呼吸はリズムよく、鼻で吸って口から吐くんだ！",
      "startTime": 10.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　はぁ、はぁ……呼吸……リズムよく……\nひっ、ひっ、ふー、ひっ、ひっ、ふー……",
      "startTime": 21.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ！　それは違う呼吸法だ！",
      "startTime": 26.3248062451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "きつい……けど、だんだん気持ち良くなってきました\nこれがランナーズハイというやつですね……！",
      "startTime": 34.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか楽しくなってきたかも……！\n今なら、どこまででも走って行けそうです……！",
      "startTime": 41.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、俺達ならどこまででも行ける！\n夕日に向かって全力ダッシュだ！",
      "startTime": 48.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "夕日なんて見えないけど、分かりました！\nうおおおおおお！",
      "startTime": 55.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3864.4463222000027,
          "startTime": 55.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……マラソンなのに……\n全力ダッシュしちゃった……さすがに、疲れました……",
      "startTime": 65.0000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すまない、俺も応援していたらテンションが上がって\nつい熱くなってしまった",
      "startTime": 74.8935486087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、私が悪いんです……\nやる気が空回りして、気持ちばかり焦っちゃって……",
      "startTime": 81.0666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "マラソンするって決まってから、変に気負って\nちゃんと走り切れるのか、ずっと不安で……",
      "startTime": 92.2000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか？　自分からマラソンに立候補したって\n聞いたから、てっきり自信があるんだと思っていたよ",
      "startTime": 100.5666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "自信なんてないです。ただ……瑠依ちゃんや優ちゃんに\n認めてもらいたくて挑戦しようと思ったんです",
      "startTime": 109.6666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "……私、たまに思うんです。瑠依ちゃんや優ちゃんから\n子供扱いされてるんじゃないかって……",
      "startTime": 119.8281200905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも私のことは対等な仲間だと思ってくれてるって\n頭では分かってるんです",
      "startTime": 128.4666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私は一番年下だから、二人に気を遣われて\n特別扱いされてるって感じることもあって……",
      "startTime": 137.5666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "すみれは今回の挑戦で、自分は子供じゃない……\n瑠依や優と対等な存在だと証明したいのか",
      "startTime": 146.5666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "はい……だから、絶対完走したいんです\n自分の力で最後までやり遂げたいんです",
      "startTime": 157.2000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そんな風に思っていたのか……。なら、気休めかも\nしれないが、神社で成功祈願をしてみるのはどうだ？",
      "startTime": 165.4666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね。せっかく神社に来たんだし\n改めて意志を固めるためにも、お参りしたいです",
      "startTime": 175.666675059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "決まりだ。一緒に神様にお願いしよう\nすみれが自分を信じて、最後まで走り切れるように",
      "startTime": 183.366675059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "神社でお参りしたら気分が落ち着きました\n今なら気負わずに走れそうな気がします",
      "startTime": 193.566675059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それなら良かった\nじゃあ、そろそろ休憩も終わりにしようか",
      "startTime": 198.766675059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "練習再開ですね！　今日はまだまだ走りますよ～\n……あれ？",
      "startTime": 207.666675059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、見て下さい！\nあそこの売店にあるキツネのストラップ！",
      "startTime": 211.5000083923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "神社だから、お稲荷様繋がりなのかな？\nすっごく可愛いキツネさんです",
      "startTime": 218.8000083923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "CMで子ギツネ役をやるから、なんだか\n親近感がわきますね。つい目が行っちゃいました",
      "startTime": 225.0000083923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "キツネのストラップか……。これも何かの縁だ\nお守りがわりに、俺からすみれにプレゼントするよ",
      "startTime": 234.4333417256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon"
    },
